---
<section class="committed">
  <div class="committed__text">
    <h2 class="committed__heading">Committed to Helping</h2>
    <p class="committed__body">
      Medicare is the federal health insurance program available to Americans 65 and older, as well
      as certain younger individuals with disabilities. While it provides essential coverage,
      <strong>Medicare alone doesn't cover everything.</strong> The choices you make during
      enrollment can affect your healthcare costs and access for years to come.
    </p>
    <p class="committed__body">
      Choosing the right combination of plans, carriers, and coverage isn't always simple. That's
      where having a dedicated Medicare broker on your side makes <strong>all the difference.</strong>
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="committed__plans">
    <div class="plan-card">
      <img src="/images/plan-a-icon.png" alt="Hospital icon" class="plan-card__icon" />
      <div>
        <p class="plan-card__title"><strong>Plan A</strong></p>
        <p class="plan-card__desc">Hospital and Inpatient Care</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="plan-card">
      <img src="/images/plan-b-icon.png" alt="Doctor icon" class="plan-card__icon" />
      <div>
        <p class="plan-card__title"><strong>Plan B</strong></p>
        <p class="plan-card__desc">Doctor Visits and Outpatient Care</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="plan-card">
      <img src="/images/plan-d-icon.png" alt="Prescription icon" class="plan-card__icon" />
      <div>
        <p class="plan-card__title"><strong>Plan D</strong></p>
        <p class="plan-card__desc">Prescription Drug Coverage</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .committed {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 33.8%; /* ~649/1920 */
    gap: 3.5rem;
    padding: 4rem var(--page-padding);
    max-width: var(--max-width);
    margin: 0 auto;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .committed__heading {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 2.5vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.15;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .committed__body {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.15vw, 1.25rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    max-width: 65ch;
  }

  /* ── Plans cards ── */
  .committed__plans {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }

  .plan-card {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    background-color: var(--color-card-tan);
    padding: 1.5rem 1.25rem;
  }

  .plan-card__icon {
    width: 5rem; /* ~80px */
    height: auto;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    object-fit: contain;
  }

  .plan-card__title {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.25vw, 1.5rem);
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .plan-card__desc {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: clamp(0.9rem, 1.1vw, 1.25rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .committed {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .committed {
      gap: 2rem;
      padding: 3rem var(--page-padding);
    }

    .plan-card {
      padding: 1.25rem 1rem;
    }
  }
</style>
